<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pinked" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pinked,</orth> pierced in small holes, reticulated: <cit><quote>railed upon me till her p. porringer fell off her head,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 4, 50</bibl></cit>. cf. <emph>Unpinked</emph> in <bibl n="shak. shr 4.1.136" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 1, 136</bibl>.
